<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_92c4ab2f-48f5-4d14-8cbf-cfeae694a3a8" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>J1P1</sptc><title id="_35236c76-f648-46b2-94dd-901417ffbdf8">Operational energy use and greenhouse gas emissions</title><archive-num>2019: JP1</archive-num><subclause id="_ead98fe9-5719-4a89-bcee-63a5a0c45e03" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_c4a63a03-b4cb-4d81-8111-cddda4048d7b">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>A building, other than a Class 4 part of a building, including its <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1456_25.0.0.xml#_242ba975-4cdf-4b84-9f41-b8d524ee17c2" id="_5ba8599c-fde7-4c53-884c-b0b050688da4" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">services</xref>, must have features that—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_f17b2d72-9fcb-40dc-9fa9-faadfe56bb02">facilitate the efficient use of energy and near zero operational greenhouse gas emissions appropriate to—<ol><li>the function and use of the building; and</li><li>the level of human comfort required for the building use; and</li></ol></li><li id="_03b4c95f-aa62-42df-83af-2bdff6c73183">for the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1225_1.8.0.xml#_26276791-20ad-4404-951f-29b5bff0ff80" id="_8681389b-9779-4969-adfa-02074e906c65" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">conditioned space</xref>, achieve an hourly <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1429_4.0.0.xml#_044c235a-5f51-4bc7-9eb9-7cfba1a0f023" id="_cf2e6c02-4bb5-4e24-bc05-fa5934bc81f0" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">regulated energy</xref> consumption and associated greenhouse gas emission, averaged over the annual <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1341_0.5.0.xml#_22178a20-4ed7-4cee-8507-b36346202638" id="_f8a0af50-b6b9-4004-95e3-6c1284de1fa0" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">hours of operation</xref>, of not more than—<ol><li>for a Class 6 building, 40 kJ/m².hr and 4 g of CO<sub id="_cce7552b-49c7-4f2b-b6de-5c0aa7e57205">2</sub>-e/m<sup id="_34d783c7-0468-4481-8626-1d045be5653e">2</sup>.hr; and</li><li>for a Class 5, 7b, 8 or 9a building other than a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1512_27.0.0.xml#_d1b612a5-df98-4406-ba1e-237f837e1061" id="_84933ce0-1b8c-4757-ae5a-36672d09db49" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">ward area</xref>, or a Class 9b <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1447_0.6.0.xml#_23515733-4511-421a-8c89-650d33e5f6e4" id="_d7c39aeb-fb85-4540-8f69-b80174903d63" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">school</xref>, 22 kJ/m².hr and 2.2 g of CO<sub id="_f22969b8-1129-4d0b-864d-62a176d85d5c">2</sub>-e/m<sup id="_1a42f8e3-4027-4ebf-a6c0-ba940ef4c0ad">2</sup>.hr; and</li><li>for all other building classifications, 8 kJ/m².hr and 1 g of CO<sub id="_5c4dfaf3-1b42-4144-8916-9d0c162d6365">2</sub>-e/m<sup id="_00f49201-2ed6-4675-a5f7-3f32964770f1">2</sup>.hr.</li></ol></li></ol></subclause></clause>